name: Mycellar
tagline: Allows you to manage the wines in your wine cellar and remember ones you've had and liked.
body:
# **MyCellar**
Allows you to manage the wines in your wine cellar.  You can enter the wines you have or have had previously and 
then display what you have currently in your cellar.

This is a simple application to test out Bootstrap, KnockOut and Node.js interactions. The site is hosted currently on http://balontz.atwebpages.com.
